      "headline": "Why We Anthropomorphize AI (And Why It Matters)",
      "description": "We can't help treating AI like a person. Understanding why reveals something important about both AI and ourselves. Javier del Puerto examines the cognitive and evolutionary roots of anthropomorphism, why it intensifies when interacting with language models, and what the tendency tells us about the coming cognitive transition — the era in which synthetic minds become a permanent feature of human social life.",
